225
00:18:34,690 --> 00:18:35,420
Nhanh thật.

226
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:41,310
Ryota.

227
00:18:42,250 --> 00:18:45,390
Hay quá vào rồi.

228
00:18:48,890 --> 00:18:50,460
Hay lắm, làm tốt lắm, Miyagi.

229
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:53,900
